      <hedline>
        <hl1>Boom Box</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Stephen S Power says he has decided to wait before buying Replay or TiVo television after reading Michael Lewis's August 13 article (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I've been thinking about buying a Replay or a TiVo. But after reading Michael Lewis's article (Aug. 13), I've decided to wait until someone invents a complementary and equally subversive device -- one that prevents Replay and TiVo from packaging my viewing habits for resale. Why pay to be spied on? I'd sooner let some network suit go through my trash.</p>
        <p>Stephen S. Power  Maplewood, N.J.</p>
      </block>
